Ontology Specification Draft

Abstract

The Battery Production and Characterization Ontology (BPCO) was developed in the project DigiBatMat. It describes production and analysis processes used in battery research. The project was funded by the German Federal Ministry of Education and Research (FKZ 03XP0367D).
